    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The solution is this:\r\n\r\n```\r\ninstantsearch({searchParameters: {hitsPerPage: 3}})\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo that no matter if you use our widgets you can always set it at the top level.",
